

We need to be able to:


* Render a card from data
  - render a rectangle with choice of colour
  - render a striped fill
  - render a squiggle
  - render a diamond
  - render a full card
* Create a grid indexing system
  - render a full grid of cards
* Select/Unselect a card
* Game logic
  - check for valid sets
  - check for invalid sets (give error message)
* Remove cards and add new cards
* Media queries and mobile friendly
* Alternative controls, arrow keys and grid on keyboard

